### 1. 내부 API - 주문 알림 발송 (핵심!)
### delivery-service가 호출하는 것 시뮬레이션
POST http://localhost:19700/internal/api/v1/notifications/order-alert
Content-Type: application/json
X-Internal-Request: true

{
  "orderId": "11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111",
  "totalDurationMinutes": 390,
  "totalDistanceKm": 428,
  "waypointNames": ["경기남부 센터", "대전광역시 센터", "대구광역시 센터"]
}

### 2. 내부 API - 헤더 없음 (403 떠야 함)
POST http://localhost:19700/internal/api/v1/notifications/order-alert
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderId": "11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111",
  "totalDurationMinutes": 180,
  "totalDistanceKm": 400,
  "waypointNames": ["대전 허브"]
}

### 3. 슬랙 직접 발송
POST http://localhost:19700/api/v1/notifications/slack
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
X-User-Role: MASTER

{
  "receiverSlackId": "슬랙아이디",
  "messageContent": "테스트 메시지입니다",
  "relatedOrderId": "11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111"
}

### 4. 슬랙 메시지 목록 조회
GET http://localhost:19700/api/v1/notifications/slack
X-User-Id: 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
X-User-Role: MASTER

### 5. AI 메시지 목록 조회
GET http://localhost:19700/api/v1/notifications/ai
X-User-Id: 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
X-User-Role: MASTER

### 6. 슬랙 메시지 삭제
DELETE http://localhost:19700/api/v1/notifications/slack/8867dd6d-8504-4c46-bb86-94ee3b46d1a6
X-User-Id: 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
X-User-Role: MASTER

### 7. 없는 슬랙 메시지 조회 (404)
GET http://localhost:19700/api/v1/notifications/slack/99999999-9999-9999-9999-999999999999
X-User-Id: 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
X-User-Role: MASTER